reviewText: Good film with Morgan Fairchild but it is not the one I expected.  But OK
DVD arrived in fine condition n plays great.
The DVD, Street of Dreams, was an okay movie. The main selling factor was Morgan Faircheilf The price fit the type of movie it was.
The breathtakingly beautiful Morgan Fairchild rules in the mistaken identity action,adventure. It was well worth watching just to see Morgan again!!!
